name: Unidentified_Mixtwirk
content: This male Mixtwirk and his Rodian companion were in the Stock Lights cantina when Cryle Cavv first explained to his nephew Sienn Sconn that he wanted to steal a Star Destroyer. The Mixtwirk tried to eavesdrop on the conversation but Cavv grabbed him by the antennae and forced the two to leave the cantina.
